hopobject.body: About a year more invigorating synonym Based on the polling, they then ranked a child's connection to nature on a scale of the lowest, -2, to the highest, 2, and considered 1.5 a "realistic and achievable" target based on children who visit RSPB nature reserves. The percentage of UK children over the 1.5 score was 21%, while girls were at 27% compared to boys at 16%. Scotland had the highest percentage over 1.5, at 27%, falling to 25% in Northern Ireland, 24% in London, 21% in England and 13% in Wales.
